<h2>Welcome</h2>

<p>Mettle makes it really easy for you to compare big data sets so you can test you database and ETL processes quickly and accurately.</p>

<p>We have made it really easy to get started straight away and you can <a href='/try'>compare 2 CSV files</a> using only your browser.  We think this is a good thing because you can work with confidential data without needing to worry about sending out of your compant over the internet or dealing with any messy paperwork.</p>

<p>Getting started could not be easier.  Just <a href='/try'>click here</a> and follow 4 simple steps to run your first test.<p>

